                <head>77. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d77fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Affairs, Staff Material, Middle East File, Box 98, Meetings File,
                        12/1/79 <gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss> re Iran. Secret. The meeting
                        took place in the White House Situation Room. <persName corresp="#p_CJ_1"
                            >Carter</persName> wrote “Zbig, J,” in the upper right corner.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1979-12-03T09:00:00-05:00" to="1979-12-03T10:15:00-05:00">December
                            3, 1979, 9–10:15 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Iran</item>
                </list>
